- What is a segment-tree/interval-tree
- What can it be used for?
    - interval with min/max/sum/...
    - an interval of length n, tree height of log(n)
- How to construct a segment-tree keeping track of min of the interval
    https://www.lintcode.com/en/problem/segment-tree-build/
- How to update a tree node
    https://www.lintcode.com/en/problem/segment-tree-modify/
- How to query within a segment-tree
    https://www.lintcode.com/en/problem/segment-tree-query/

Important:
- How to add/remove a tree node
    Cannot add/remove node within the interval

